Text: Coming from Nigeria through the Sahara desert was beyond unbelievable surviving
  most terrible situations and deadly dramatic, hoping that getting to Libya would
  be more better and easier. Still it was more worst from the Libya youths, who claims
  to be a deadly rebels and they're called the Axeman boys, always shooting different
  types of guns weapons. Life in Libya wasn't friendly, full of different dramatic
  problems.
